Games/IL2Device/Link version 0.3.1
==========================

Games::IL2Device::Link and Games::IL2Device::Constants are two perl
modules to help communicating with IL2 Forgotten Battles client (>=
2.01) using the 'devicelink' connection. For more information on
devicelinks see 'DeviceLink.txt' in your IL2 Forgotten battles
directory.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

